Minimum lot size: 20,000 square feet. Except that if served by an approved public
or community water or sewage disposal system, lot size may be reduced to 10,000
square feet.
llm_outputs.rationale: This section specifies the minimum lot size requirements for the O&I district.
llm_outputs.answer: 20,000 sq ft; 10,000 sq ft if served by public water/sewer
